“提康德罗加号”航母1972年5月5日（周五）把阿波罗十六号指令舱运到加利福尼亚州[[聖地牙哥_(加利福尼亞州)|圣地亚哥]]附近的[[北岛海军航空站|北岛海军航空站]]。5月8日，航空站机库用于清空残留毒理反应控制系统燃油的地面设备爆炸，46人送往医院观察24至48小时，大部分属于吸入有毒烟雾，手推车翻倒压身以致膝盖骨折的技师伤势最重。上方76米的机库屋顶炸开大洞，约40扇窗户玻璃震碎，指令舱面板出现7.6厘米裂缝。<ref>{{cite news | title = 46 injured in Apollo 16 explosion | newspaper = Lodi News-Sentinel | access-date = 2021-12-18 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=0eUzAAAAIBAJ&pg=1722%2C2797182 | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | date = 1972-05-08 | pages = 1–[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=0eUzAAAAIBAJ&pg=6132%2C2805357 2] | archive-date = 2022-02-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220201050639/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=0eUzAAAAIBAJ&pg=1722%2C2797182 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Apollo blast: 46 hurt | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=03lWAAAAIBAJ&pg=6904%2C1961609 | access-date = 2021-12-18 | agency = [[澳聯社|Australian Associated Press]]-[[路透社|Reuters]] | newspaper = [[雪梨晨鋒報|The Sydney Morning Herald]] | date = 1972-05-09 | page = 1 | archive-date = 2020-12-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201231213229/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=03lWAAAAIBAJ&pg=6904%2C1961609 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

“卡斯帕号”所有权1973年11月从航空航天局移交[[史密森尼学会|史密森尼学会]]<ref name="hardware">{{cite web | title = Apollo/Skylab ASTP and Shuttle Orbiter Major End Items | date = 1978-03 | publisher = NASA | page = 6 | archive-date = 2021-12-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211214010759/https://s3.documentcloud.org/documents/6473665/Apollo-Skylab-ASTP-and-Shuttle-Orbiter-Major-End.pdf | access-date = 2021-12-18 | dead-url = no | format = PDF | url = https://s3.documentcloud.org/documents/6473665/Apollo-Skylab-ASTP-and-Shuttle-Orbiter-Major-End.pdf }}</ref>，现在亚拉巴马州[[亨茨维尔_(阿拉巴马州)|亨茨维尔]]附近的[[美国太空和火箭中心|美国太空和火箭中心]]展出<ref>{{cite web | url = https://airandspace.si.edu/explore-and-learn/topics/apollo/apollo-program/spacecraft/location/cm.cfm | title = Location of Apollo Command Modules | publisher = National Air and Space Museum | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211117020944/https://airandspace.si.edu/explore-and-learn/topics/apollo/apollo-program/spacecraft/location/cm.cfm | archive-date = 2021-11-17 | access-date = 2021-12-18 }}</ref>。登月舱上升段1972年4月24日同服务与指令舱分离后失控，绕月飞行约一年后下落不明<ref name=":0" />。S-IVB三级火箭撞击月表后四十余年下落不明，直至2016年1月[[月球勘测轨道飞行器|月球勘测轨道飞行器]]在[[島海|島海]]发现，位于[[哥白尼环形山|哥白尼环形山]]西南约260公里<ref name="fullsummary" /><ref name=":0">{{cite web | title = Apollo – Current Locations | url = https://nssdc.gsfc.nasa.gov/planetary/lunar/apolloloc.html | publisher = NASA | access-date = 2021-12-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211201054921/https://nssdc.gsfc.nasa.gov/planetary/lunar/apolloloc.html | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-12-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | publisher = Space.com | date = 2016-01-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211103172313/https://www.space.com/31503-apollo-16-moon-rocket-crash-site-photo.html | access-date = 2016-01-05 | url = https://www.space.com/31503-apollo-16-moon-rocket-crash-site-photo.html | title = Moon Mystery Solved! Apollo Rocket Impact Site Finally Found | work = Space | first = Jesse | last = Emspak | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-11-03 }}</ref>。

